-- Monte Paschi 5-yr bond to yield 275 basis points over midswap - lead
-- 
-- Tue Mar 25, 2014 10:24AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, March 25 (Reuters) - A five-year bond Monte dei Paschi di Siena <BMPS.MI> offered on Tuesday will pay a yield of 275 basis points over the midswap rate, one of the lead managers of the issue said.

The yield guidance for the 1 billion-euro ($1.4 billion)senior unsecured bond was initially set at around 290 basis points.